#   na "But Lilly..."
    na "Pero Lilly..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1367
translate spanish ep023_crew_6ca8f766:

#   l "No Mom, I don’t know more."
    l "No mamá, no sé más."

# game/episode023.rpy:1369
translate spanish ep023_crew_57a201bd:

#   l "No Nadya, I don’t know more."
    l "No Nadya, no sé más."

# game/episode023.rpy:1370
translate spanish ep023_crew_3af5c59d:

#   l "I can barely look you in the eye as it is."
    l "Apenas puedo mirarte a los ojos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1376
translate spanish ep023_crew_562ae6df:

#   e "Absolutely not."
    e "Por supuesto que no."

# game/episode023.rpy:1377
translate spanish ep023_crew_3ce47f05:

#   e "I want to know as little as possible about it."
    e "Quiero saber lo menos posible al respecto."

# game/episode023.rpy:1379
translate spanish ep023_crew_f6c1cfa3:

#   e "What you’re doing is wrong and you both know it."
    e "Lo que estás haciendo está mal y ambos lo sabéis."

# game/episode023.rpy:1380
translate spanish ep023_crew_126280b8:

#   e "I don’t want to be complicit in your behavior."
    e "No quiero ser cómplice de tu comportamiento."

# game/episode023.rpy:1383
translate spanish ep023_crew_67128a67:

#   na "But Eva..."
    na "Pero Eva..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1386
translate spanish ep023_crew_2fde8a80:

#   e "No Mom, I don’t know more."
    e "No mamá, no sé más."

# game/episode023.rpy:1388
translate spanish ep023_crew_ac42ffde:

#   e "No Nadya, I don’t know more."
    e "No Nadya, no sé más."

# game/episode023.rpy:1389
translate spanish ep023_crew_69b5b5bb:

#   e "I can barely look you in the eye as it is."
    e "Apenas puedo mirarte a los ojos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1391
translate spanish ep023_crew_cbad1f14:

#   "On that sour note, all the girls left us."
    "En esa nota amarga, todas las chicas nos dejaron."

# game/episode023.rpy:1392
translate spanish ep023_crew_fc5824f3:

#   "Nadya was still sitting on my bed, looking a little forlorn."
    "Nadya seguía sentada en mi cama, con cara de desamparo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1393
translate spanish ep023_crew_810d8bd6:

#   na "I wanted to tell you earlier in person, but you were just out of the medbay."
    na "Quería decírtelo antes en persona, pero acababas de salir de la enfermería."

# game/episode023.rpy:1395
translate spanish ep023_crew_f0fc7517:

#   na "And then Lilly and Aven made their announcements..."
    na "Y entonces Lilly y Aven hicieron sus anuncios..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1397
translate spanish ep023_crew_2f70b940:

#   na "And then Lilly made her announcement..."
    na "Y entonces Lilly hizo su anuncio..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1399
translate spanish ep023_crew_c96ac942:

#   na "And then Aven made her announcement..."
    na "Y entonces Aven hizo su anuncio..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1400
translate spanish ep023_crew_cf099f60:

#   c "You were worried I wouldn’t be able to take the shock?"
    c "¿Te preocupaba que no pudiera soportar el shock?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1402
translate spanish ep023_crew_610711a1:

#   na "Maybe...{w} Something like that."
    na "Tal vez...{w} Algo así."

# game/episode023.rpy:1403
translate spanish ep023_crew_96f19fbc:

#   na "Maybe you’d be disappointed..."
    na "Tal vez te decepcionaría..."

# game/episode023.rpy:1404
translate spanish ep023_crew_fc1d68d9:

#   c "Disappointed?"
    c "¿Decepcionado?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1406
translate spanish ep023_crew_d3d2a588:

#   c "I’m over the moon, Mom!"
    c "¡Estoy en la luna, mamá!"

# game/episode023.rpy:1408
translate spanish ep023_crew_7e206ad0:

#   c "I’m over the moon!"
    c "Estoy encantada."

# game/episode023.rpy:1409
translate spanish ep023_crew_46c0697a:

#   c "We talked it over, didn’t we?"
    c "Lo hablamos, ¿no?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1410
translate spanish ep023_crew_2724c85e:

#   c "We both decided we wanted this and I still do."
    c "Ambos decidimos que queríamos esto y yo sigo queriéndolo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1411
translate spanish ep023_crew_8acef7ce:

#   c "You don’t know how happy you’ve made me."
    c "No sabes lo feliz que me has hecho."

# game/episode023.rpy:1413
translate spanish ep023_crew_93495d47:

#   na "Sorry, [p_name_short], I don’t know what came over me."
    na "Lo siento, [p_name_short], no sé lo que me pasó."

# game/episode023.rpy:1414
translate spanish ep023_crew_4c8f87ca:

#   na "With all that happened on Petrarch and you being in a coma, I just started to panic."
    na "Con todo lo que pasó en Petrarca y tú en coma, me entró el pánico."

# game/episode023.rpy:1415
translate spanish ep023_crew_8c85b57b:

#   na "What if you’d come out of that coma all changed."
    na "¿Y si hubieras salido del coma cambiado?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1416
translate spanish ep023_crew_6d199864:

#   na "We’d be all alone in the galaxy, running from the Sovereignty and my pregnancy would be a risk, a liability even."
    na "Estaríamos solos en la galaxia, huyendo del Soberano, y mi embarazo sería un riesgo, incluso un lastre."

# game/episode023.rpy:1417
translate spanish ep023_crew_38163117:

#   c "I would never think something like that."
    c "Nunca pensaría algo así."

# game/episode023.rpy:1418
translate spanish ep023_crew_dfd98ce4:

#   na "I know, and I’m sorry."
    na "Lo sé, y lo siento."

# game/episode023.rpy:1419
translate spanish ep023_crew_478dc73f:

#   na "I just don’t want to lose you."
    na "No quiero perderte."

# game/episode023.rpy:1420
translate spanish ep023_crew_f6ea7185:

#   c "You won’t and I won’t let anything happen to you and the baby."
    c "No lo harás y no dejaré que os pase nada a ti y al bebé."

# game/episode023.rpy:1421
translate spanish ep023_crew_ff845d9d:

#   c "Shall we talk about happy things now, there’s been enough doom and gloom for one day, I’d say."
    c "Hablemos ahora de cosas felices, yo diría que ya ha habido suficiente pesimismo por hoy."

# game/episode023.rpy:1423
translate spanish ep023_crew_d5a29f5b:

#   na "I agree."
    na "Estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1424
translate spanish ep023_crew_23d8719d:

#   c "How long have you known?"
    c "¿Desde cuándo lo sabes?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1425
translate spanish ep023_crew_b6f7749e:

#   na "A few weeks now."
    na "Desde hace unas semanas."

# game/episode023.rpy:1426
translate spanish ep023_crew_1eb64a23:

#   na "I did a test when we were back on the Bastard, taking turns watching over you."
    na "Hice una prueba cuando estábamos de vuelta en el Bastardo, turnándonos para vigilarte."

# game/episode023.rpy:1428
translate spanish ep023_crew_b8c800aa:

#   na "I was so happy at first, [p_name_short], becoming a mother again!"
    na "Al principio estaba tan feliz, [p_name_short] ¡volviendo a ser madre!"

# game/episode023.rpy:1430
translate spanish ep023_crew_6352beed:

#   na "I was so happy at first, [p_name_short], becoming a mother!"
    na "Estaba tan feliz al principio, [p_name_short] ¡convertirme en madre!"

# game/episode023.rpy:1432
translate spanish ep023_crew_caa59837:

#   na "Only after I told you the news at your bedside, did the worry set in."
    na "Sólo cuando te di la noticia junto a tu cama, empezó la preocupación."

# game/episode023.rpy:1434
translate spanish ep023_crew_6fc4b47c:

#   na "The girl’s reaction just now was what I feared too."
    na "La reacción de la chica hace un momento era lo que yo también temía."

# game/episode023.rpy:1435
translate spanish ep023_crew_847acb4f:

#   c "Don’t worry, they’ll come around."
    c "No te preocupes, volverán en sí."

# game/episode023.rpy:1437
translate spanish ep023_crew_326035d3:

#   na "Aven’s reaction just now was what I feared too."
    na "La reacción de Aven hace un momento era lo que yo también temía."

# game/episode023.rpy:1438
translate spanish ep023_crew_7ae0bbbc:

#   c "Don’t worry, she’ll come around."
    c "No te preocupes, ya entrará en razón."

# game/episode023.rpy:1440
translate spanish ep023_crew_4f8c38e8:

#   na "Lilly’s reaction just now was what I feared too."
    na "La reacción de Lilly hace un momento era lo que yo también temía."

# game/episode023.rpy:1443
translate spanish ep023_crew_76baf0b0:

#   na "Eva’s reaction just now was what I feared too."
    na "La reacción de Eva hace un momento era lo que yo también temía."

# game/episode023.rpy:1446
translate spanish ep023_crew_a4c59678:

#   na "I’m not so sure."
    na "No estoy tan seguro."

# game/episode023.rpy:1447
translate spanish ep023_crew_bed8d552:

#   c "They might not accept our love, but they’ll have to deal with the fact that you’re pregnant sooner or later."
    c "Puede que no acepten nuestro amor, pero tarde o temprano tendrán que asumir que estás embarazada."

# game/episode023.rpy:1448
translate spanish ep023_crew_3ed1b816:

#   na "I hope so, [p_name_short], I really hope so."
    na "Eso espero, [p_name_short], de verdad que lo espero."

# game/episode023.rpy:1449
translate spanish ep023_crew_56c3579f:

#   c "We’ll get through this."
    c "Lo superaremos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1450
translate spanish ep023_crew_598fe70e:

#   c "Our child is going to grow up in peace with a loving mother and father."
    c "Nuestro hijo va a crecer en paz con una madre y un padre cariñosos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1453
translate spanish ep023_crew_4a05bada:

#   "My mother smiled hopefully and rested her head against my shoulder."
    "Mi madre sonrió esperanzada y apoyó la cabeza en mi hombro."

# game/episode023.rpy:1455
translate spanish ep023_crew_aee88a27:

#   "Nadya smiled hopefully and rested her head against my shoulder."
    "Nadya sonrió esperanzada y apoyó la cabeza en mi hombro."

# game/episode023.rpy:1457
translate spanish ep023_crew_18902aa3:

#   na "Could you perhaps visit my quarters later?"
    na "¿Podría visitar mis aposentos más tarde?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1458
translate spanish ep023_crew_8657d262:

#   na "To spend the night, I mean."
    na "Para pasar la noche, quiero decir."

# game/episode023.rpy:1459
translate spanish ep023_crew_64584fdf:

#   c "Of course I’ll come."
    c "Por supuesto que iré."

# game/episode023.rpy:1460
translate spanish ep023_crew_4c71d833:

#   na "Thank you."
    na "Gracias, señor."

# game/episode023.rpy:1461
translate spanish ep023_crew_53d9d2ea:

#   na "I just want you close after being separated for so long."
    na "Sólo te quiero cerca después de estar separados tanto tiempo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1463
translate spanish ep023_crew_7d43a4a6:

#   "We sat in silence until we both decided it was time to brave the outside world."
    "Nos sentamos en silencio hasta que ambos decidimos que era hora de salir al mundo exterior."

# game/episode023.rpy:1470
translate spanish ep023_crew_6eb8a8b7:

#   av "Now you have to tell us all about your pregnancy, Mom."
    av "Ahora tienes que contarnos todo sobre tu embarazo, mamá."

# game/episode023.rpy:1472
translate spanish ep023_crew_c7cefeac:

#   av "Now you have to tell us all about your pregnancy, Nadya."
    av "Ahora tienes que contarnos todo sobre tu embarazo, Nadya."

# game/episode023.rpy:1473
translate spanish ep023_crew_204d0ca6:

#   e "Yes, how long have you known?!"
    e "Sí, ¡¿desde cuándo lo sabes?!"

# game/episode023.rpy:1474
translate spanish ep023_crew_5115fd37:

#   "I left the girls talking exuberantly about their mother’s happy news and prepared to inform the rest of the crew."
    "Dejé a las niñas hablando exultantes sobre la feliz noticia de su madre y me dispuse a informar al resto de la tripulación."

# game/episode023.rpy:1476
translate spanish ep023_crew_8a18dd1c:

#   c "Right, that’s all for now, thank you all."
    c "Bien, eso es todo por ahora, gracias a todos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1478
translate spanish ep023_crew_2eeff45f:

#   "The girls left my quarters and I got busy preparing to inform the rest of the crew."
    "Las chicas salieron de mis aposentos y yo me ocupé de informar al resto de la tripulación."

# game/episode023.rpy:1153
translate spanish ep023_crew_ba3b14ce_1:

#   na "We are in love."
    na "Estamos enamorados."

# game/episode023.rpy:1185
translate spanish ep023_crew_ba3b14ce_2:

#   na "We are in love."
    na "Estamos enamorados."

# game/episode023.rpy:1362
translate spanish ep023_crew_52247b60_1:

#   c "Fair enough, suit yourself."
    c "Me parece justo, como quieras."

# game/episode023.rpy:1381
translate spanish ep023_crew_52247b60_2:

#   c "Fair enough, suit yourself."
    c "Me parece justo, como quieras."

# game/episode023.rpy:1373
translate spanish ep023_crew_0d9fe021_1:

#   e "The same goes for me."
    e "Lo mismo me ocurre a mí."

# game/episode023.rpy:1441
translate spanish ep023_crew_7ae0bbbc_1:

#   c "Don’t worry, she’ll come around."
    c "No te preocupes, ya entrará en razón."

# game/episode023.rpy:1444
translate spanish ep023_crew_7ae0bbbc_2:

#   c "Don’t worry, she’ll come around."
    c "No te preocupes, ya entrará en razón."

# game/episode023.rpy:1485
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_1200c6d0:

#   "The following morning, Aven let me know that one of our first diplomatic overtures had borne fruit."
    "A la mañana siguiente, Aven me comunicó que una de nuestras primeras gestiones diplomáticas había dado sus frutos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1486
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_d7992da9:

#   "The Tubloshi had responded almost immediately to our invitation and arranged for a rendezvous in a neutral location."
    "Los Tubloshi respondieron casi de inmediato a nuestra invitación y concertaron una cita en un lugar neutral."

# game/episode023.rpy:1487
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_4eeaff58:

#   "I joined Céline and her on the bridge as we made our approach."
    "Me uní a Céline y a ella en el puente mientras nos acercábamos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1488
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_717fed81:

#   c "It’s happening."
    c "Está ocurriendo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1489
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_18e204b6:

#   c "Did they seem friendly in their message?"
    c "¿Parecían amistosos en su mensaje?"

# game/episode023.rpy:1491
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_26f80052:

#   av "They were formal, but nothing overtly friendly, nor hostile."
    av "Eran formales, pero nada abiertamente amistoso, ni hostil."

# game/episode023.rpy:1492
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_2564a2dc:

#   c "I guess we’ll know soon enough."
    c "Supongo que pronto lo sabremos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1493
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_e0b2338e:

#   c "Be ready to jump as soon as you notice something out of the ordinary, Céline."
    c "Prepárate para saltar en cuanto notes algo fuera de lo normal, Céline."

# game/episode023.rpy:1495
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_1605c824:

#   ce "I will."
    ce "Lo haré."

# game/episode023.rpy:1496
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_7164ea82:

#   c "Weapons at the ready, Aven."
    c "Armas listas, Aven."

# game/episode023.rpy:1498
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_5ebe1729:

#   "Almost immediately after we entered the agreed-upon system, a large warship dropped out of hyperspace."
    "Casi inmediatamente después de entrar en el sistema acordado, una gran nave de guerra salió del hiperespacio."

# game/episode023.rpy:1500
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_21b75fbf:

#   av "That’s them."
    av "Son ellos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1501
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_cd3f6780:

#   ce "They’re hailing us already."
    ce "Ya nos están llamando."

# game/episode023.rpy:1502
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_624bee8f:

#   c "Put them through."
    c "Pásalos."

# game/episode023.rpy:1503
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_4a6a1489:

#   "A familiar sounding voice resonated through the bridge."
    "Una voz familiar resonó en el puente."

# game/episode023.rpy:1504
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_836beadd:

#   ha "Greetings, [p_name] of the Humans."
    ha "Saludos, [p_name] de los Humanos</b0>."

# game/episode023.rpy:1505
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_926e6f41:

#   c "Greetings, Mighty Warriors of the Tubloshi, I’m overjoyed that you honor us with your presence."
    c "Saludos, Poderosos Guerreros del Tubloshi, estoy encantado de que nos honréis con vuestra presencia."

# game/episode023.rpy:1507
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_856672f0:

#   ha "As you well should, [p_name] of the Humans."
    ha "Como bien deberías, [p_name] de los Humanos</b0>."

# game/episode023.rpy:1508
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_e9da77e6:

#   ha "We have received your missive and have reluctantly agreed to discuss its contents."
    ha "Hemos recibido su misiva y hemos accedido de mala gana a discutir su contenido."

# game/episode023.rpy:1509
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_2457721a:

#   ha "You may dock with our ship and await our coming in the vestibule."
    ha "Pueden atracar con nuestro barco y esperar nuestra llegada en el vestíbulo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1511
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_2065df64:

#   ha "The honor is ours, [p_name] of the Humans."
    ha "El honor es nuestro, [p_name] de los Humanos</b0>."

# game/episode023.rpy:1512
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_53a988ab:

#   ha "We have received your missive and would like to discuss its content in the comfort of our ship."
    ha "Hemos recibido su misiva y nos gustaría discutir su contenido en la comodidad de nuestro barco."

# game/episode023.rpy:1513
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_7ffb1a84:

#   ha "You may dock with our ship and we will welcome you personally."
    ha "Puede atracar con nuestro barco y le daremos la bienvenida personalmente."

# game/episode023.rpy:1514
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_811a6e8d:

#   c "Of course, we’ll dock immediately."
    c "Por supuesto, atracaremos inmediatamente."

# game/episode023.rpy:1516
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_90add027:

#   "The Tubloshi severed the connection and Céline started our approach of the warship."
    "El Tubloshi cortó la conexión y Céline inició nuestra aproximación al buque de guerra."

# game/episode023.rpy:1517
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_fb811cea:

#   "The voice over the comms was that of Hannah, the redheaded translator we encountered before."
    "La voz por el comunicador era la de Hannah, la traductora pelirroja que encontramos antes."

# game/episode023.rpy:1519
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_9b259529:

#   "Acknowledging her presence on the comms would have probably been construed as some sort of slight directed at the Tubloshi, so I hoped to be able to get a private conversation with her while on the warship."
    "Reconocer su presencia en el comunicador probablemente habría sido interpretado como algún tipo de desaire dirigido a la Tubloshi, así que esperaba poder mantener una conversación privada con ella mientras estuviera en la nave de guerra."

# game/episode023.rpy:1521
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_1e08f39c:

#   "Ziv and Aven were to accompany me this time and we geared up the moment the Bastard docked with the Tubloshi warship."
    "Ziv y Aven iban a acompañarme esta vez y nos preparamos en cuanto el Bastardo atracó con la nave de guerra Tubloshi."

# game/episode023.rpy:1522
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_2ab87300:

#   "The ship looked just as I remembered, angular and militaristic, much like the Tubloshi themselves."
    "La nave tenía el mismo aspecto que recordaba, angulosa y militarista, como los propios Tubloshi."

# game/episode023.rpy:1523
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_f112f407:

#   "The corridor was empty and the inner hatch closed."
    "El pasillo estaba vacío y la escotilla interior cerrada."

# game/episode023.rpy:1524
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_3f4cf032:

#   "We didn’t dare to advance without permission from the Tubloshi, so we waited in the hallway."
    "No nos atrevimos a avanzar sin permiso del Tubloshi, así que esperamos en el pasillo."

# game/episode023.rpy:1526
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_53b41cc4:

#   "They kept us waiting for a long time, matching the reluctance I sensed when the Tubloshi spoke to us on the comms."
    "Nos hicieron esperar mucho tiempo, igualando la reticencia que percibí cuando el Tubloshi nos habló por el comunicador."

# game/episode023.rpy:1531
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_2a2f47cc:

#   "Finally the doors opened and two giant Tubloshi warriors came in, with Hannah in front."
    "Por fin se abrieron las puertas y entraron dos gigantescos guerreros Tubloshi, con Hannah al frente."

# game/episode023.rpy:1533
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_8c904655:

#   "Luckily, we didn’t have to wait long, as the doors opened almost immediately after we had disembarked."
    "Por suerte, no tuvimos que esperar mucho, ya que las puertas se abrieron casi inmediatamente después de desembarcar."

# game/episode023.rpy:1538
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_f3050506:

#   "Two giant Tubloshi warriors came in, with Hannah in front."
    "Dos gigantescos guerreros Tubloshi entraron, con Hannah al frente."

# game/episode023.rpy:1544
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_9442faa0:

#   "Hannah was still a vision, her red hair almost glowing in the artificial light of the ship."
    "Hannah seguía siendo una visión, su pelo rojo casi brillaba bajo la luz artificial del barco."

# game/episode023.rpy:1547
translate spanish ep023_tubloshi_e914a281:

#   "She was also visibly pregnant."
    "También estaba visiblemente embarazada."

# game/episode023.rpy:1548
